Name&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8nq1zmz&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">•&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m23lu\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模型规模扩展：</span>基于Qwen3-32B微调的SFT模型在AIME2024上达92.71%，HMMT2025达89.38%，验证数据引擎对更大模型的有效性。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6vg8nq1zmz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 7 []&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mj6xwp7b1jpb&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 3 []&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8ot1jkv&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8nq1zmz&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">•&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m23lu\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">基座模型泛化性：</span>基于Qwen3-8B-Base微调的SFT模型取得了与Logics-STEM-8B-SFT相近的表现，证明该数据引擎可独立为STEM领域的后训练提供支持，不依赖现有SFT模型。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px 24px;text-align: left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6vg8nq1zmz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;3 7 []&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mj6xwp7b1jpb&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;2 3 []&quot;,&quot;data-mpa-action-id&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8ot1jkv&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8nq1zmz&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">•&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m23lu\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">训练范式通用性：</span>“错题”驱动合成数据在持续 SFT（Continual SFT）与RLVR中均取得近乎一致增益，1:1混合比例下效果媲美纯RL训练。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.275\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0H3REshgy4mHYIv5RicQgCAic2jJRNCKmT3nhKAwianL7bnRLr1asianzt43jzRgQtyLuvW33Y5A2RdxZCgqvlrELA/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"578\" data-cropsely2=\"187\" data-imgfileid=\"502280139\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=103d9b32&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0H3REshgy4mHYIv5RicQgCAic2jJRNCKmT3nhKAwianL7bnRLr1asianzt43jzRgQtyLuvW33Y5A2RdxZCgqvlrELA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D9\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: left;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m1wtk\">Logics-STEM项目坚持全链路开源，对外发布：</span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6vg8nq1zmz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8nq1zmz&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">•&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m1wtk\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模型权重：</span>HuggingFace已开源8B规模模型权重、SFT/RL双版本</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: left;\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6vg8nq1zmz\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px 8px 24px; text-align: left;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;mpa-font-style&quot;:&quot;mj6vg8nq1zmz&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">•&nbsp;</span></span></span></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m1wtk\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">训练数据：</span>1.6M精选版长CoT数据集与5.3M完整版（即将发布），附带难度标签与学科分类</span></span></p>\n  <div style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: left;\">\n   <span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m1wtk\">我们相信，“好数据”比“大算力”更稀缺。此次开源大规模长 CoT 数据，是希望把高质量推理数据的获取门槛降到最低，让更多研究者都能便捷使用、共同验证与迭代，促进推理模型整体能力的持续进步。</span>\n   <div style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;margin-top: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"2 3 []\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6vg8ot1jkv\">\n    <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-bottom: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-aistatus=\"1\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img js_img_placeholder wx_img_placeholder\" data-ratio=\"0.275\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"background-color: transparent;\" data-croporisrc=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/0H3REshgy4mHYIv5RicQgCAic2jJRNCKmT7ibdeE6vfj2H1b6mmibu5lHKicSMhJ00VhDjXwolqTPMBP8EMfn1qN1ew/0?wx_fmt=png&amp;from=appmsg\" data-cropselx2=\"562\" data-cropsely2=\"182\" data-imgfileid=\"502280140\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dafc162d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F0H3REshgy4mHYIv5RicQgCAic2jJRNCKmT7ibdeE6vfj2H1b6mmibu5lHKicSMhJ00VhDjXwolqTPMBP8EMfn1qN1ew%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg%23imgIndex%3D10\"></p>\n    <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;margin-bottom: 24px;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9mplg\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6va6pp1m63\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Logics-STEM通过数据-算法协同设计，在STEM推理任务中实现了开源模型的性能新突破。其核心价值在于将后训练视为分布匹配问题，并系统化地利用失败信号驱动数据合成，从而高效缩小提议分布与目标分布的差距。未来工作将探索更大规模模型、Agentic Reasoning能力，并持续优化RL算法的稳定性与可扩展性。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">项目链接</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">技术报告:&nbsp;</span>Logics-STEM: Empowering LLM Reasoning via Failure-Driven Post-Training and Document Knowledge Enhancement（<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.01562v1）\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/2601.01562v1）</a></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">模型与数据:&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-8B-SFT（<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-8B-SFT）\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-8B-SFT）</a></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-8B-RL（<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-8B-RL）\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-8B-RL）</a></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset-Open-1.6M（<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset-Open-1.6M）\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset-Open-1.6M）</a></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin:0px 8px;outline:0px;letter-spacing:0.544px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, &quot;system-ui&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"outline: 0px;font-size: 15px;font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m5zb\"><span data-mpa-action-id=\"mfyyefxfvfa\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span style=\"\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;font-size: 13px;\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xwp6c1y00\"><span leaf=\"\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6xx2321253\" style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mj6xx23k13zr\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset-Open-5.3M（<a href=\"https://huggingface.co/datasets/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset-Open-5.3M）\" target=\"_blank\">https://huggingface.co/datasets/Logics-MLLM/Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset-Open-5.3M）</a></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;text-align: right;\"><span data-type=\"text\" mpa-font-style=\"mj6vds9m1mio\" style=\"font-family: Optima-Regular, PingFangTC-light;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\" data-mpa-action-id=\"mg0i8exto7d\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">点击</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 128, 255);font-weight: bold;font-style: italic;\">“阅读原文”</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">查看技术报告</span></span></span></span></p>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "阿里与复旦联合推出 Logics-STEM 框架，通过“错题”驱动的数据-算法协同范式，在 8B 参数量级实现了 STEM 推理能力的 SOTA 突破并全链路开源。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "阿里与复旦联合推出 Logics-STEM 框架，通过“错题”驱动的数据-算法协同范式，在 8B 参数量级实现了 STEM 推理能力的 SOTA 突破并全链路开源。",
  "summary": "本文详细介绍了由阿里集团与复旦大学联合研发的 Logics-STEM 推理模型。该研究将 LLM 的后训练过程形式化为分布匹配问题，创新性地提出了“错题驱动”的后训练框架。通过识别模型在 SFT 阶段的失败案例，结合知识增强检索与双验证数据合成技术，显式修正模型分布与目标分布的偏差。实验表明，Logics-STEM-8B 在 AIME、GPQA 等权威 STEM 基准测试中表现卓越，超越了同尺寸开源模型。项目同时开源了高质量的 2.2M 长思维链（CoT）数据集、模型权重及代码，为社区研究复杂推理提供了重要基础设施。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "将 SFT-RL 后训练流程形式化为分布匹配问题，建立数据与算法的协同闭环。",
      "explanation": "通过第一阶段构建高质量提议分布，第二阶段利用“错题”驱动进行目标分布对齐，从理论上保证了模型梯度更新方向与理想目标的更高对齐度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "构建了目前开源社区规模最大、质量最高的长 CoT 语料库 Logics-STEM-SFT-Dataset。",
      "explanation": "数据集经过五阶段净化处理，涵盖 2.2M 精选样本，通过难度感知采样平衡了推理密度与多样性，有效避免了初级推理能力的遗忘。"
    },
    {
      "point": "采用“错题”驱动的知识增强检索与双验证合成机制，精准提升模型薄弱环节。",
      "explanation": "针对模型失败案例检索外部知识库，利用 DeepSeek-R1 合成并经双验证机制筛选的高质量数据，显著优化了高难度区域的采样权重。"
    },
    {
      "point": "高质量数据蒸馏在中小规模模型上可部分替代强化学习（RL）训练。",
      "explanation": "实验显示 Logics-STEM-8B-SFT 性能已媲美部分 RL 模型，证明了在资源受限场景下，优化数据质量是提升推理能力的有效路径。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "Logics-STEM 首次将 SFT-RL 后训练流程形式化为分布匹配问题，提出两阶段协同优化框架。",
    "我们相信，'好数据'比'大算力'更稀缺。此次开源大规模长 CoT 数据，是希望把高质量推理数据的获取门槛降到最低。",
